data.description: WATERFRONT PROPERTY! Priced to Sell! No HOA! Imagine your evenings with friends or your mornings with a cup of coffee, surrounded by the tranquil beauty of the Anclote River's gentle Inlet. Across the water, an island plays host to local wildlife, offering a delightful soundtrack to your daily escape. Ready to set sail? Your boat can have you in the Gulf's open waters in just 35 minutes. Step into your new sanctuary, where three bedrooms await, along with a versatile bonus room – perfect for an office, cozy TV nook, or a playful haven for your inner child. The house is filled with updates, boasting a clean and fresh look complemented by brand-new flooring. And guess what? A shiny, new roof was just installed in November 2023, ensuring your home stands strong and proud. While there might not be a picnic table under a massive tree (we had to save a little space for your personal touch!), there's plenty of room for laughter and connection. This residence isn't just a house; it's an invitation to the quintessential Florida lifestyle. With the Anclote River Park and the Anclote Gulf Park just around the corner, your next chapter is waiting to unfold. Don't miss the chance to make this waterfront haven your own – a home that promises more than just four walls; it's an everyday vacation retreat!
